== Colonies & Outposts ==
No colonies or outposts have ever been established in Level 180. 

== Entrances & Exits ==
=== Entrances ===
* No-clipping over the fence in [[Level 204]] will sometimes bring one to Level 180 rather than [[Level 10]]; and
* Entering a house in [[Level 55]] will sometimes bring one here. 

=== Exits ===
* No-clipping through the bed of a lake with a marble bottom will bring one to [[Level 181]];
* No-clipping over a fence in a meadow will sometimes bring one to [[Level 204]];
* Following a river in the Forest will bring one to [[Level 173]]; and
* Speaking the "Angel of God" prayer is alleged to bring one to a level of their own choice. 




